    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Portable stands with a very small top intended to hold a candle or lamp; usually having a round or shaped top supported on a central pillar and with a tripod base.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
